flowchart TD
    START{Who is inviting?}

    START -->|User linked to member| A1[User A is linked to a member]
    START -->|Admin or Manager| A2[Admin/Manager selects a member]

    A1 --> B[Invite User B by email]
    A2 --> B

    B --> C[Email sent with invitation link]
    C --> D[User B clicks link]
    D --> E{Has an account?}

    E -->|Yes| F[Log in]
    E -->|No| G[Register + verify email]

    F --> H[Accept invitation page]
    G --> H

    H --> I[Choose relationship type]
    I --> J["type: self | relative"]
    J --> K["Edit description (e.g. mother, uncle)"]
    K --> L[Confirm]
    L --> M[user_members entry created]
    M --> N[User B is now linked to the member]
